{"tid":440764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估地方] 剛滿18歲企圖硬上少女　臨陣提槍卻不舉","createTime":"2017-10-19T05:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T05:49:58.000Z","uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cfb348001800c45f7cf39c6e08992b50b6f2af6a","tid":440764,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171018/640_bb75101891a68d9089c6af0c56cda47b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171018%2F640_bb75101891a68d9089c6af0c56cda47b.jpg&h=e5f345d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年西洋情人前夕，新北市一名剛滿18歲的陳姓男子邀約一名輕度智能障礙的15歲女網友出遊，卻涉嫌對她伸出狼爪，沒想到臨陣提槍卻不舉，最後改用手指性侵。新北地檢署今依對身心障礙女子強制性交罪起訴陳男。<br />\n起訴指出，去年2月13日陳男邀約一名輕度智障的少女到他朋友家聚會，2人到達陳男的朋友家時，才知他正好外出，陳男竟將少女帶到該棟公寓頂樓，要求少女幫他口交但遭拒絕，竟企圖硬上，沒想到臨陣提槍卻不舉，只好改用手指性侵少女。<br />\n少女回家後難過地不停哭泣，家人起疑詢問，才揭發陳男淫行。<br />\n陳男到案否認犯行，只承認當天2人有一起出去，但發現朋友外出，就改去逛夜市了。不過檢察官勘驗2人的臉書對話內容，顯示案發後少女曾向陳男表示「當晚因太緊張，才不敢口交」，因此不採信陳男辯詞，今將陳男起訴。（葉晴煦／新北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20171018/1224805/%E5%89%9B%E6%BB%BF18%E6%AD%B2%E4%BC%81%E5%9C%96%E7%A1%AC%E4%B8%8A%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E3%80%80%E8%87%A8%E9%99%A3%E6%8F%90%E6%A7%8D%E5%8D%BB%E4%B8%8D%E8%88%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flocal%2F20171018%2F1224805%2F%25E5%2589%259B%25E6%25BB%25BF18%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E4%25BC%2581%25E5%259C%2596%25E7%25A1%25AC%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%2587%25A8%25E9%2599%25A3%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%25A7%258D%25E5%258D%25BB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2588%2589&d=lqIhu9U%2BCmjjKJE3AlZIxDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3384aca2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20171018/1224805/%E5%89%9B%E6%BB%BF18%E6%AD%B2%E4%BC%81%E5%9C%96%E7%A1%AC%E4%B8%8A%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E3%80%80%E8%87%A8%E9%99%A3%E6%8F%90%E6%A7%8D%E5%8D%BB%E4%B8%8D%E8%88%89</a>"},{"pid":"96025046e9aee9b10b84050d01e2571713bf68af","tid":440764,"uid":32298,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:38:01.000Z","msg":"輕度智障都識上網...唔怪得連登會員啲質素..."},{"pid":"013b6ba07005cc37ccc937daf4d4c4c239536f62","tid":440764,"uid":14103,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:43:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輕度智障都識上網...唔怪得連登會員啲質素...</blockquote><br />\n我都好同情你嘅遭遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177dbc6c48f8ba251fd7a0bc3733bdec1724b06c","tid":440764,"uid":39800,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>輕度智障都識上網...唔怪得連登會員啲質素...</blockquote><br />\n我都好同情你嘅遭遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n😂👍🏻"},{"pid":"f512967651c6a6eea8a4b254bd748eeaea3b4f75","tid":440764,"uid":36898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:48:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>輕度智障都識上網...唔怪得連登會員啲質素...</blockquote><br />\n我都好同情你嘅遭遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f776d10421905866ead8ad4588f1106c9b90ab93","tid":440764,"uid":58852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:49:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>輕度智障都識上網...唔怪得連登會員啲質素...</blockquote><br />\n我都好同情你嘅遭遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同病相憐"}]}